sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant COL as ccxt collector
    participant REDIS as Redis Stream ingest:events:v1
    participant CG as Consumer Group cg.vault_writer
    participant WRITER as Vault writer consumer
    participant VAULT as VAULT partitions and manifest
    participant DLQ as Redis Stream ingest:events:dlq:v1

    COL->>COL: Build envelope and dedup_key
    COL->>REDIS: XADD event

    WRITER->>REDIS: XREADGROUP from cg.vault_writer
    REDIS-->>WRITER: event batch
    WRITER->>WRITER: Validate schema and check idempotency

    alt write succeeds
        WRITER->>VAULT: Insert tick or connection_event
        WRITER->>REDIS: XACK processed IDs
    else write fails repeatedly
        WRITER->>DLQ: XADD original event plus error metadata
        WRITER->>REDIS: XACK failed IDs after DLQ handoff
    end
